A startup founder invites students to a lunchtime pitch session. Concurrently, workshops on networking etiquette begin in the adjoining classroom, and an alumni panel discusses how to prepare for technical interviews. Students compare swag items like water bottles and phone chargers. A whiteboard lists employers who are scheduling same-day interviews. After the event, a post-event survey link flashes on the monitors near the exit.
